The mask in question has right click unlimited FD, 1.7 cast time (.2 seconds longer than the spell) BUT it has INSTANT recast. No more seeing &quot;Groshuk has fallen to the ground&quot; and having to try and hang on for a small eternity getting your ass beat before you can try again. Not only that but with an item for FD this frees up a spell slot which is very handy.<br>
This mask is ridiculously easy to get too, so now VI has for whatever reason decided to shaft us in a huge way and handicap us with an outrageous disadvantage. I have finally gotten mad enough about this stupid game to sign up on their damn message board and send in a letter of complaint. I'd urge all the rest of you to do the same, it's bad enough having people say I can't pull any good because I can't FD as fast as a monk but now I'm going to hear it about other SKs.<br>
<br>
Groshuk Hedcrushur<br>
