Maybe a better example of my complaint is to say that with the people I used to play with I pulled for most raids we did. While pulling I die a lot because my FD doesn't recycle fast enough to give me a second chance usually if it fails, this mask would save me a lot of deaths (meaning exp too) and would allow me to keep pulling faster and steadier meaning the other people on the raid are happier because they aren't sitting around waiting for me to recover yet again.<br>
Enchanters are a class that dies as much or more as pullers from what I've seen, wouldn't you be pissed if you were denied an item that would cut down significantly on that?<br>
Maeve you say we shouldn't complain about needing to swap spells but at least casters and healers get  break to do it either during a fight or while pulls are happening. If I am pulling and doing a good job of it I never have a break, I am either fighting or bringing back the next mob so it is something I would appreciate.<br>
